location.fullValue: Chatfield Plan, Arabella on the Prairie

data.description: Welcome to this spacious 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in a peaceful neighborhood thats just a stones throw away from the brand new elementary school. The interior boasts generously sized bedrooms, perfect for relaxation and personal space. The recently updated kitchen offers a contemporary style, ideal for culinary enthusiasts. Additionally, indulge in the privacy of a first floor primary suite with the luxury of a garden tub in the primary bathroom for ultimate relaxation. Outside, a massive backyard with a wooden playset awaits, providing ample space for outdoor activities and gatherings. New paint, kitchen upgrades and new LVP flooring all in 2022. Welcome home to a perfect blend of style and comfort for your family!
